import React from "react";
import { MDBCard,MDBCardHeader, MDBCardBody, MDBCardTitle, MDBBtn, MDBRow, MDBCol, MDBIcon, MDBContainer} from 'mdbreact';



function Post() {

    return(
        <MDBCol className="post pr-3 pb-4" lg="7">
            <MDBContainer fluid className="post_container">
                <MDBRow>
                    <MDBCol md="6">
                        <MDBBtn className="post_button" href="#" color="default" size="lg">
                            Add Post
                        </MDBBtn>
                    </MDBCol>
                    <MDBCol md="6">
                        <MDBBtn className="post_button" href="#" color="default" size="lg">
                            Add Interview Experience
                        </MDBBtn>
                    </MDBCol>
                </MDBRow>
                <MDBRow className="mt-5">
                    <MDBCol class>

                    </MDBCol>
                </MDBRow>
            </MDBContainer>
        </MDBCol>
    )
}

export default Post
